PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Energy, Mines and Resources of Ronald D. Grantham, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a director of the Atomic Energy of Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John Schlosser, whose term has expired.
